{"tid":1155902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"留下遺書對不起丈夫女兒　女子竹園南邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-05-15T09:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T05:12:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d50b1d64ce14376a1d88df8baa855c57274a42c3","tid":1155902,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"黃大仙竹園南邨華園樓，今午(15日)2時27分，一名中年女子被人發現由高處墮下，倒臥地上，消防及救護員接報到場，證實女子已傷重死亡。警方在場撿獲相信是死者的銀包，內有證件及一張紙，寫上「對不起老公，我先行一步　女：對唔住Sorry」，事件初步無可疑，正調查女子墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=82a59d4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190515/mobile/bkn-20190515145858816-0515_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190515%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190515145858816-0515_00822_001.html&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=11b1773f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190515/mobile/bkn-20190515145858816-0515_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4052055b43dcdaf85d123178cafda419b11c569f","tid":1155902,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"又唔寫發生咩事 你屋企人點幫你報仇呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adcf10885c34dec520eed15e20e2ae0d3be9e17","tid":1155902,"uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190515/large/1557906000_740e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt